---
By: Annamalai Swami
Locus:
  Page: 203
  Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Grace
---
Most people have many desires which they want to fulfill. But some rare
people tell God： “I want nothing. Make me desireless, that is my only
desire.” Such a one will be a fit instrument to receive grace. ...The one
who will get the most grace is the one who is completely desireless.
